"tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":331,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":331,"voiceId":"event166-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"I had no idea you guys made a promise like that...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event166-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"After that, I picked up the bass so that I could be in a band someday with Hana-chan.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event166-02-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"And you two not only met, you even both got up on stage at the Budokan... It's pretty incredible stuff if you think about it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event166-02-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"I still remember hating the fact that I had to move~, fufu.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event166-02-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"I bet we would've made a band if you hadn't.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"event166-02-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"You guys in a band, huh...? For some reason, I have this image of you two performing on the streets.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event166-02-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Fufu, I'm sure that kind of a future might've been possible, but it's just a what-if.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event166-02-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishClo